message: Jun Matsumoto is no longer active as [[Arashi]] and he will now act individually as an actor. Arashi was not popular before. But thanks to Jun Matsumoto drama, I think Arashi was able to gain popularity. And if you go to the Arashi page,On January 27, 2019, Arashi announced that group activities will be suspended as of December 31, 2020.
Jun Matsumoto's publications have been deleted, and you're only going to write about Arashi, not Jun Matsumoto's personal information.
The description is too crude and long, so I'll return it to the original version. That's all written on the Arashi page.
